<hr>
<h4>Lozar's Map Piece</h4>
When trying to obtain Lozar's map piece, you will have to deal with Wormbrain. Simply pay him 10,000 Coins for the map piece to avoid any combat.
<hr>
<h4>Melzar's Map Piece</h4>
Obtaining Melzar's map piece means you have to go through Melzar's Maze. Only specific pre-determined monsters drop keys:
<ul>
  <li>the small Zombie Rat with a long tail,</li>
  <li>the Ghost with a hood, no cape, and a single tendril coming out of each shoulder,</li>
  <li>the Skeleton with a tiny round shield,</li>
  <li>one of two indistinguishable Zombies,</li>
  <li>Melzar the Mad,</li>
  <li>a Lesser Demon.</li>
</ul>
Each of these can be TFK'd for the key drop.
