<hr>
<h4>Elvarg</h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8">
    Elvarg is a very tough green dragon. Her dragonfire will always very quickly drain your prayer points, and if not protected against, will also quickly drain all your combat stats. Even with dragonfire protection, the breath can hit 1,000 - 1,500 typeless damage which cannot be recoiled. Her melee attack is marginally weaker but can be recoiled. Using some form of life-point boosting is therefore heavily recommended.
    <br /><br />
    Luckily, Elvarg does not give Combat XP when killed, allowing you to fight her normally instead of having to recoil 10,000 LP.
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-sm-4">
    {% include monster.html monster=site.data.monsters.elvarg %}
  </div>
</div>
